ams%3FAt%202Gether-International%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20answer%2C%20and%20it%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20extraordinary.This%20year%2C%20through%20our%20Accessible%20Ecosystem%20initiative%20in%20partnership%20with%20IDB%20Lab%2C%20we%20brought%20our%20mission%20to%20Latin%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20supporting%20entrepreneurs%20with%20disabilities%20and%20innovators%20creating%20inclusive%2C%20tech-driven%20solutions.We%20designed%20two%20programs%20to%20meet%20founders%20where%20they%20are%3A%20Venture%20Labs%2C%20a%204-week%20incubator%2C%20helps%20early-stage%20entrepreneurs%20move%20from%20idea%20to%20validation.%20Accelerator%2C%20a%2010-week%20program%2C%20helps%20founders%20develop%20scalable%20businesses%20to%20grow%20and%20pitch%20for%20funding.These%20founders%20show%20every%20day%20that%20inclusion%20and%20innovation%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%20The%20first%20cycle%20of%20Venture%20Labs%20made%20that%20crystal%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.2gether-international.org%2Fnews%2Ftogether-we-rise-the-accessible-ecosystem-through-the-eyes-of-our-founders%22%20class%3D%22cta-link%20no-padding%20_1%20_2%22%3ERead%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20role%3D%22listitem%22%20class%3D%22blog-card-copy%20w-dyn-item%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-w-id%3D%22303f2ed5-dfd5-8ded-b90b-3828217686d1%22%20alt%3D%22%22%20sizes%3D%22100vw%22%20class%3D%22image%20card%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22post-type%20text-style-all-caps%22%3EJune%2030%2C%202025%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch3%20class%3D%22text-h4%22%3ETop%20Tips%20for%20Disabled%20Individuals%20Interested%20in%20Entrepreneurship%3A%20Insights%20from%20a%20Forbes%20Accessibility%20100%20Honoree%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22paragraph%22%3EEntrepreneurship%20is%20a%20powerful%20and%20empowering%20path%20for%20Disabled%20individuals%2C%20offering%20autonomy%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20the%20chance%20to%20innovate%20based%20on%20lived%20experience.%20Drawing%20on%20the%20story%20and%20impact%20of%202Gether-Internation